0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"舊衫會引發應該係塵蟎 買一罐果d殺蟎霧炸下屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過，不過屋企有貓有小朋友好難實行<br />\n<br />\n利申，對貓&amp;貓毛無敏感"},{"pid":"1eebfe6f201e7000629967b4e4d0ee37aec344aa","tid":780541,"uid":170891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26e5d9a2a8b1a6ea8dd3e1b081c90f5f412babf1","tid":780541,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"我以前鼻敏感都好嚴重 去過專科政府個一隻 等左兩年先睇到一次 跟住一年一次<br />\n每次都係叫我用鹽水洗鼻<br />\n<br />\n之後就每朝都洗鼻，一星期換一次床單 買左部吸床既吸塵機 吸塵蟎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係發作就食粒佳力天<br />\n而家好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"洗鼻間唔中有做，不過自己衰嫌麻煩維持唔到，巴打覺得有用嘅話等我堅持吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家都係發作就食claritin或者zyrtec, 多數都幾work"},{"pid":"e59984d4e6efd195d799c4a7caf2ca70093f8205","tid":780541,"uid":122521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:26:14.000Z","msg":"我都有二十年鼻敏感，但我就堅持唔用西藥（食/噴），每次一想打風下雨就好凖時發作，及對香味好敏感。<br />\n近期我開始用維他命（蜂膠+維a)發覺有改善，無發作咁多。"},{"pid":"cbda0185d030a601d19d1bfb8d49b2c2e960868d","tid":780541,"uid":136327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"由細到大都有鼻敏感，有幾次岀國之後就斷咗陣<br />\n番到香港又黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家間房長著屌米空氣清新機，又好番唔少<br />\n個人認為香港空氣差應該都係原因之一"},{"pid":"dadeeb54ca9e9b7a083373f1b11c7cc32adde9a0","tid":780541,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"食藥得啦...."},{"pid":"40419d8bb7537fdd53c4d1c5dbe57cc2c16cbff2","tid":780541,"uid":18668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"試下完全唔飲凍飲先"},{"pid":"d19534a0d5ff04307b38422ca438ba85cfbdc788","tid":780541,"uid":80845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"好嚴重 訓邊邊 個邊就塞<br />\n一開始有洗 慢慢已經由佢算<br />\n習慣左<br />\n<br />\n對我就大影響係想學潛水但嚴重到落一米幾水深已經feel到再落會穿耳膜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623028bc463ba662a51e8367a323ae3a2327d8fc","tid":780541,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e7d46bb0307d5b100c6fc7d6841a92e8483409","tid":780541,"uid":143656,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T20:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/040313_b2e2cacd343eb89f841c04f56c9af744.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F040313_b2e2cacd343eb89f841c04f56c9af744.png&h=52e42830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nE枝野醫生開俾我 <br />\n本身塞左半年 用左5日即刻通哂<br />\n醫生話係安全改善ge方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:18:44.000Z","msg":"我都係靠呢枝"},{"pid":"92be6e7eb3d657eba5d870cf51e068d067fc649b","tid":780541,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d19534a0d5ff04307b38422ca438ba85cfbdc788","tid":780541,"uid":80845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"好嚴重 訓邊邊 個邊就塞<br />\n一開始有洗 慢慢已經由佢算<br />\n習慣左<br />\n<br />\n對我就大影響係想學潛水但嚴重到落一米幾水深已經feel到再落會穿耳膜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"同鼻敏感冇關wor"}]}